Package: image.CornerDetectionHarris
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of the Harris Corner Detection for Images
Description: An implementation of the Harris Corner Detection for detecting relevant points in images as described in the paper: "An Analysis and Implementation of the Harris Corner Detector". The algorithm is explained at <doi:10.5201/ipol.2018.229>. 
Maintainer: Jan Wijffels <jwijffels@bnosac.be>
